## EXECUTIVE SUMMARY

Kathy A. Hart (age 78) is currently receiving skilled nursing and rehabilitation care at Gilmer Connected Care in Gilmer, TX following XLIF spinal surgery at UT Health Tyler. She was transferred from Ashley Center at Grande (Tyler, TX) to Gilmer Connected Care on or around October 10, 2025, with coordination by Amy McClellon, her local care coordinator.

**Critical Status:** Kathy is experiencing significant anxiety about her financial situation and lack of control over her accounts. A care plan meeting is scheduled for Thursday, October 23, 2025 at 2:00 PM CT to determine discharge timeline and home care requirements.

**Financial Status:** Accounts are secure but in transition. Chase accounts remain active with POA access granted October 15, 2025. Austin Bank account activation is in progress with external account verification initiated October 20, 2025.

